d initial SIS costs. * **Timeline**:\n* NYISO prepares the draft Scope of Work (SIS Scope) for review by TPAS and OC: \\~1–2 months. ... *\"NYISO prepares and tenders a SISA to the Customer...The Transmission Developer is required to provide a study deposit of either $40,000 (if the Transmission Developer is hiring a third-party consultant to perform the analytical portions ... * **Refundability**:"
